# =============================================================================
# .trivyignore — intentional suppressions for this project
#
# Each entry is a Trivy finding ID. Findings suppressed here are acceptable
# for a local/demo environment and are documented with a reason below.
# Review before deploying to production.
# =============================================================================

# DS-0026: No HEALTHCHECK instruction in Dockerfile
# Health checks are defined in docker-compose.yml per service (e.g., sqlserver,
# redis, rabbitmq all have explicit healthcheck blocks). Adding HEALTHCHECK to
# every Dockerfile would duplicate that config and is unnecessary when the
# orchestration layer manages container health.
DS-0026
